  "description": "<p><u><em><strong>IT'S NEVER TOO LATE FOR A NEW BEGINNING OF YOUR LIFE</strong></em></u></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Love to Travel ? Looking for change of environment ? Just ORD? Just graduate?</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Be part of the world’s leading Sales &amp; Marketing Company and work with International clients across different countries! With a dynamic team that strives for high standard campaign execution, bringing great opportunities and unlimited growth.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Role:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Face to face interaction with people</li>\n  <li>Building customer relationship and maintaining positive brand awareness.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Overseas Travelling Opportunities</li>\n  <li>1 to 1 Mentorship &amp; Coaching</li>\n  <li>Fun and Vibrant Environment</li>\n  <li>Career Advancement</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong> :</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Team Player</li>\n  <li>Keen Learner</li>\n  <li>Good Command of English</li>\n  <li>No experience needed!</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>APPLY NOW!</strong></u></p>",
